Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:37.27,Ep_Title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,600)}Trick or Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:41.10,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:45.07,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Is Taichi Kabasawa at school right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:47.74,Default,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi Kabasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:48.91,Default,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:50.42,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,He's famous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:52.65,Default,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't come to class anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.88,Default,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,He got cocky by putting the name of his college\N out there, but he's actually scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.95,Default,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,People online might treat him like a god,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:01.70,Default,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,but among us, he's famous for being \Na coward who's desperate for recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.51,Default,MAN A,0000,0000,0000,,Kakihana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:11.80,Default,MAN A,0000,0000,0000,,We know you're in there, Kakihana-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:17.74,Default,MAN A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kakihana! You need to \Npay back what you borrowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.13,Default,MAN A,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your parents teach you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.39,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, taxi driver? \NTurning yourself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.66,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You here to turn yourself in, huh? \NWhat'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.19,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.69,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your brother today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:35.65,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.07,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,My brother worked the day shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.31,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,He's already done with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:40.64,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect. I'm reporting an incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:41.82,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.95,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Someone fired a gun into my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.45,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's major! Why didn't you\N call the emergency number?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.15,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.84,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'm calling my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.63,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.91,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.82,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Things get difficult when \Nyour brother's involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:57.18,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.57,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Only relatives find those \Nkinds of pranks funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:04.57,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Grandma loved that joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.84,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Say you're going out on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:07.87,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.41,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are we going inside your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:15.45,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.80,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But you're, y'know—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.72,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,this is mad awkward, and I'm not sure \Nhow to say it, but don't you have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.54,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,that Nerima high school girl \Nlocked up in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.72,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That was incredibly direct. \NBut no, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.95,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.26,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,This is the shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:36.47,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. I can't handle this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:40.45,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's all kinds of paperwork\N to fill out, procedures to follow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.97,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of rules about \Npreserving the crime scene, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.67,Default - Top,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend for this \Nto become a police case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.31,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.88,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose I go to Roppongi at night \Nand get absolutely plastered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.88,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The trains aren't running, so I call \Nfor a taxi, and you show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:56.17,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What would you think if I told you, \N"I don't intend to go home?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:05:00.34,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Or suppose I went to the barber and said, \N"Could you give me a long hairstyle?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.96,Default - Top,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:02.92,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0} truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:07.44,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Little Daimon, why did you want \Nto become a police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.40,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,To punish evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.91,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you want to punish evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.61,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.27,Flashback,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.34,Flashback,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,Kenshiro, Koshiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.49,Flashback,MOM,0000,0000,0000,,We're going out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.31,Flashback,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:29.93,Flashback,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Bring back cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.16,Flashback,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.91,Italics,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Our parents were killed \Nby a hit-and-run driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:48.27,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,By a taxi, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.99,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you can't stand the sight of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.78,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We'd catch bad guys with our own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:57.56,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my brother and I swore we'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.68,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's how it was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:00.85,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:03.72,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But now, your brother is evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:07.96,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you. It's true that my brother \Nchooses black when we play Othello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.49,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we played tag, \Nhe always wanted to be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:11.71,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.14,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother is working with Dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:18.22,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about that already. \NI asked my brother about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.30,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,He told me that he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:21.83,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.15,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:25.79,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Between you and my brother, \Nobviously I believe my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.03,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of twins do you think we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.61,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We're identical twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.87,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate Dobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.75,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After all, he's evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:37.41,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Little Daimon, I'll give you \Nan opportunity to catch Dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.66,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! That'd be huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:42.85,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But if you arrest him normally, \Nhe'd only be charged with a petty crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:45.03,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is he planning to do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:45.77,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:46.85,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.50,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working with Dobu right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:51.08,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You're evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.80,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. I'm {\i1}pretending{\i0} to work with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.31,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll just gradually become more\N evil by pretending to work with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.06,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Take a seat, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.73,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a minute, shut up and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.44,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.25,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You can speak when I ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:14.47,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, huh? He's the kind \Nof evil who stays hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:17.08,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu and Yano are rivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.62,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,And above them is their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:26.50,sign_10480_102_Boss,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:26.50,sign_10480_103_Money,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:26.50,sign_10480_104_Yano,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Yano
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:26.50,sign_10480_105_Rivals,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:26.50,sign_10480_106_Dobu,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:26.50,sign_10480_107_Money,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:23.63,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dobu and Yano's job \Nto give money to their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:26.50,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,They don't get along because \Nthey compete over the sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.80,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Sum means much or how \Nlittle money they give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:36.45,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,If you have something to say \Nor any questions, you can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.10,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who their boss is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:43.73,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, before we became cops, \NDobu was arrested for robbing a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.46,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,His boss may have been \Nthe principal offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:50.73,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. And one of Dobu's \Nassociates is your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.49,sign_11218_117_Dobu,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.49,sign_10480_103_Money,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.49,sign_10480_102_Boss,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.49,sign_11218_118_Big_Daimon,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daimon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.96,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't cut that out, I'll beat you \Nblack and blue, taxi driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:56.99,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why would my brother work with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.28,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's for money \Nor something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.79,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I think Dobu is buying off a cop so \Nit's easier for him to do his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.41,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that without evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.66,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're going to arrest Dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.67,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Then my brother will be arrested, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:14.47,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you're starting to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:16.75,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You dislike evil, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.94,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.86,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Then if your brother is doing bad things, \Nthen you've got to punish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.47,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, your sense of justice will waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:27.19,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll punish him. \NIf he's doing bad things, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.90,sign_10480_103_Money,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.90,sign_10480_102_Boss,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.90,sign_10480_107_Money,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.90,sign_10480_104_Yano - Copy,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Yano
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.90,sign_11218_117_Dobu,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.90,sign_11218_118_Big_Daimon,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daimon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.90,sign_10480_105_Rivals - Copy,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.90,sign_12161_132_Odokawa,SIGN BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.90,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm pretending to work with Dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.00,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your name's Odogawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:33.79,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:37.45,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter. You're the only one \Nwho cares about that detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.92,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Dobu's being \Npursued by a streamer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.34,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know? I'm subscribed to his channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:45.68,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a huge fan of Taichi Kabasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:47.52,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,You guys do want the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:48.77,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_12687_142_Kabasawa,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Kabasawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_10480_103_Money,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_13241_152_Dobu,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_11218_118_Big_Daimon,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Big Daimon
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_12161_132_Odokawa,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_10480_102_Boss,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_10480_107_Money,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_10480_104_Yano - Copy2,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Yano
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:55.09,sign_10480_105_Rivals - Copy,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Rivals
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.75,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Then you know about skull mask, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.71,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That guy who showed up at the cabaret club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.09,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that Dobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.78,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It actually wasn't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.94,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it was someone \Nwho stole Dobu's gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.71,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,And for some reason, he wants to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.94,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.95,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Dobu wants \Nto catch Kabasawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:12.23,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,get his gun back from skull mask, \Nand get the jump on Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:15.04,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect myself \Nfrom the mysterious skull mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:18.82,sign_13241_152_Dobu,SIGN CIRCLE TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:18.82,sign_13241_153_Odokawa,SIGN CIRCLE BOTTOM RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.82,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm pretending to work with Dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:20.33,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.89,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to work with Dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:26.29,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You should let the police \Nhandle the skull mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.60,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not actually smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.96,sign_13711_164_Shiraka,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:39.75,sign_10480_103_Money - Copy,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:39.75,sign_12687_142_Kabasawa - Copy,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Kabasawa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:39.75,sign_10480_102_Boss - Copy,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:39.75,sign_10480_107_Money,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Money
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:39.75,sign_10480_104_Yano - Copy2,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Yano
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:39.75,sign_13875_163_Goriki,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Goriki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.88,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a grudge against Dobu, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:39.75,sign_13711_164_Shiraka_S,SIGN BOTTOM LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.17,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible's happening \Nto a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.58,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I want to bring him to his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.76,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:44.45,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Getting to down to business, \NDobu is planning to rob a bank soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:47.69,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's clearly evil! \NIt'd be a repeat offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.22,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks I'll help him do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:53.75,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll arrest Dobu then, Little Daimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:58.52,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing if it's true, \Nbut you'll be arrested, too, Odokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:02.00,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. We're doing \Nthis to punish evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.28,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're the opposite of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.74,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Why not just call me good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.63,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You were really convincing, \Nbut it's hard to believe all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:18.97,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I agree. That's why I'm going to \Nkeep tracking down evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.32,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, I thought you \Nwere the kidnapper
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:25.68,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,in the Nerima missing high school girl case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.54,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Could I take a look around your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.25,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.27,Italics,RADIO,0000,0000,0000,,MPD to all stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:52.25,Italics,RADIO,0000,0000,0000,,An unidentified body has found \Nat the mouth of the Sumida River.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.19,Italics,RADIO,0000,0000,0000,,Nearby police box, please head there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.55,Italics,RADIO,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, MPD to all stations...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.60,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.94,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.53,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:04.26,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll hear you out, \Nif it means punishing evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:07.22,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Here's my special direct phone number!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.12,sign_16301_190_Shiho,SIGN TOP,0000,0000,0000,,Shiho
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.12,sign_16301_191_I_might_be_a_lit,SIGN BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,I might be a little late...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:24.12,sign_16301_192_Sorry_for_asking,SIGN WHITE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for asking to meet when you're busy \Nwith work. I'll wait as long as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.12,sign_16366_193_Sorry__just_fini,SIGN BOTTOM/BLUE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, just finished! \NI'm heading your way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.04,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:35.65,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,An unidentified body has been \Nfound in the Tokyo Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.30,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,This morning before dawn, \Nat the Shibaura Wharf in Minato Ward,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:51.02,sign_16926_197_Live,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Live
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:51.02,sign_16926_198_New_Info_from_Lo,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H09e5f0&}New Info{\c} from Location Where Body was Discovered \N{\c&H09e5f0&}Abandoned Body?{\c} Police Rushing to Identify Victim
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:51.02,sign_16926_199_Minato_Ward_Shib,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Minato Ward Shibaura Wharf
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:52.20,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,the body of a woman believed to be in \Nher teens to thirties was discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.90,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,Nearby construction workers \Nreported the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.06,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,and according to the police investigation, \Nafter being killed elsewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.00,Default - Top,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.01,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,they believe her body was dumped in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.54,Italics,NEWSCASTER,0000,0000,0000,,They believe roughly a month \Nhas passed since her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:17.50,sign_17536_207_Miho_Shirakawa,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Miho Shirakawa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:17.50,sign_17536_209_10_26__Tues_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,10/26 (Tues)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:17.50,sign_17536_211_10_27__Wed_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,10/27 (Wed)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:17.88,Italics,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,"All I can say is I'm really sorry \Nabout the trouble I caused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:23.74,Italics,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu-san told me that he doesn't \Nneed my help or money anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:30.10,sign_17838_215_10_27__Wed_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,10/27 (Wed)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.95,Italics,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,"There seemed to be some reason for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:30.10,Italics,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess this means my \Nrelationship has been dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:34.01,Italics,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll forgive me."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.32,sign_15631_176_Goriki_Clinic,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Goriki Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:41.89,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.69,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,A guy named Dobu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:48.52,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But my relationship \Nwith him has been dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:49.66,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:53.74,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa must've done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:57.54,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Odokawa-san said he'd pretend \Nto work with Dobu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.98,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:05.93,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably trying to save both you \Nand me at the same time by doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.00,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:15.73,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't pay you, but will \Nyou help me with my work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:18.70,Default,SHIRAKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Work? What work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.15,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Have you \Nforgotten what I do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.36,Default,GORIKI,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to treat Odokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:29.27,sign_19280_233_Medical_Exam_Rec,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,550)}Medical Record
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:29.27,sign_19280_234_Name__Hiroshi_Od,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,550)}Name: Hiroshi Odokawa\N Male \NDOB: May 25th, 555 \NAge: 41 years 5 months \NAddress: Nerima Ward Mukaiyamabashi, \N5-12 Irodori Heights 102
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.05,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow. Foot cramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.54,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.70,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Foot cramp. Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:46.09,sign_19726_241_Safety_First,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Safety First
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:53.39,Default,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I just got here. Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.43,Default,ICHIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.07,0:13:58.85,Default,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I don't see you, Shiho-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.95,Default,ICHIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Kakki, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.90,Default,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Shiho-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.00,Default,ICHIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. You came at just \Nthe right time, Kakki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.24,Default,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,One of my subordinates made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.01,Default,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I had to clean up after—Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:16.04,Default,KAKIHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you said I came \Nat just the right time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:24.84,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Good work. Be careful on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:27.36,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late for the \NHalloween event in Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.82,Default - Top,WOMAN A,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.82,Default,WOMAN B,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.82,Default,MAN B,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:51.86,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.79,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should be saying ow, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:58.47,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are you lookin', \Ndid your eyes disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.95,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Is this war? Love me tender.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.04,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of people tellin' me to be gentler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:06.82,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to traffic, \Neveryone does as they please,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.22,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,But "all's well that ends well" \Nain't good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:13.01,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Violence is my business, you simpleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.39,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:19.55,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Hah. "What?" So, that's your answer? \NOld man, don't make me scoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:25.90,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't apologize, I'll grab a shotgun \Nand blow your head off. Bang, bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.40,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter your brain. Right brain, left brain, \Nfrontal lobe, cerebellum, cerebrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:34.98,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,You understandin'? A heartfelt \Napology is what I'm demandin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.91,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for riding \Na scooter in this crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:43.33,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My {\i0}fault for riding a scooter? \NThat's what everyone says, but I don't agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.65,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Arguin' with every amateur \Nout here ain't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.61,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Between you and I there's \Na long, long Silk Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.59,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Too much space between us, \Nit's a mental overload.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.13,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of generalizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.59,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,and if you've matured at all, \Nwhere's the apology I'm owed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.19,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:59.06,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. Now it's win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:03.86,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Lukewarm like the one-coin canned coffee \Nyou can buy at this Halloween jamboree,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:08.72,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,cold like the coin laundries I used \Nwhen I was at the bottom of the heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.07,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Took me a while to make \Nmy point, but tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.85,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,what I wanted to say was \Nthat you'd better make things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:17.93,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,This may sound sudden, but have \Na heart. I'm sorry, my guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.41,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the day, I just want \Nsome compassion, don't be shy. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:28.40,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,People lose their minds on Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:34.00,Default,KANON,0000,0000,0000,,Did you learn the song yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.18,Default,REINA,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. How much longer do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.90,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:41.86,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head there as soon \Nas the event is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.89,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.56,Default,NIKAIDO,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that? Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.17,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.13,Default,NIKAIDO,0000,0000,0000,,Do we still have to appear \Nin events like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:54.69,Default,NIKAIDO,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't we handle our own show?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.14,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Just be patient a little longer, Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.14,0:17:00.39,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,By Christmas, you'll pull ahead \Nof everyone appearing here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.49,Default,ICHIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.00,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.39,0:17:07.89,Default,ICHIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:08.88,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.80,Default,ICHIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Running these badger games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.88,Default,NIKAIDO,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.84,Default,NIKAIDO,0000,0000,0000,,How are you gonna earn \Nmoney for the agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.13,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:19.08,Default,YAMAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. We'll talk later, Ichimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:23.39,sign_24960_305_Shibuya_Center_S,SIGN TOP LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,Shibuya Center Street
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.71,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:33.89,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on. How'd you know it was me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:37.71,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm good \Nat spotting people in a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.47,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Was it my build?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.73,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Or am I not blending in with the crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.95,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt anyone else would recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:47.99,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm impressed you're not \Ntoo ashamed to dress like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:51.12,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,It's humiliating. But I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:54.34,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you find skull mask \Non your way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:56.02,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:59.28,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were good \Nat spotting people in a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:02.01,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Not his type.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.84,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:07.89,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,How should I explain it? It's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.40,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Milk, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.71,Default,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:16.09,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,For example, once I memorize \Nthat waitress' face,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:19.82,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I could spot her in a crowd \Neven if she changes her makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.93,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What kind of power is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.96,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see auras or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.38,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's close to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:30.78,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,But when I've never seen a guy's face \Nand he's wearing a full-face mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.19,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,then I'm just like the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.57,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:39.01,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you can find \NTaichi Kabasawa in a crowd,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.61,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,but not skull mask, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:42.64,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:45.31,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:49.19,sign_26991_334_Taichi_Kabasawa_,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi Kabasawa \N{\c&H868686&\fs16}@kbsw_t – 1 hour ago \N{\c}{\fs\c&H2a2a2a&\b0}I'm in Shibuya now!!\N If you see Dobu, let me know!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:53.37,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start by checking out \Nanything that seems credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.32,sign_27167_336_koya___koya_came,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,koya {\c&H8a8a8a&}@koya_camera411 \NReplying to: @kbsw_t \N{\b0\c&H000000&}I saw Dobu wearing a skull mask\Nin front of 109!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:56.97,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Kabasawa's here in Shibuya, too, \Nso we may be able to get them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.65,sign_27226_343_Kabasawa_Believe,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Kabasawa Believer {\c&H8a8a8a&}@kbsw_god32871 \NReplying to: @kbsw_t \N{\c&H000000&\b0}I'm more interested in meeting our god!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.75,Default,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we have to go on patrol \Nfor these fools again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:18.09,Default,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's so fun about this? Everyone's just\N making asses of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:22.18,Default,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,All these guys got their costumes \Na while ago, did their makeup at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.47,Default,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,and took the train in all the way \Nfrom the boonies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.12,Default,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,When they go home, and\N take off the costumes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:28.15,Default,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,and makeup, I wonder if they\N wish they were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.55,Default,KENSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:34.08,Flashback,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother is working with Dobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:38.62,Default,KOSHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.32,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,According to recent information, \Nhe's around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:48.59,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,They've even uploaded photos, \Nso it should be fairly credible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:49.75,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:58.41,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we found him so easily. \NThe internet is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:02.36,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Since skull mask is targeting you, \Nstand a little farther away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.43,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:04.39,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:06.60,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,and if I get the chance, \NI'll drag him into a deserted alleyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.84,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a gun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.97,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,He'd {\i1}better{\i0} have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:25.65,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,So persistent, so drawn out, \Nmy ringtone's imposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:28.98,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dealing with a lot \Nover here. Submission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:33.30,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Addiction. Wish I could take my medicine \Nand go to bed, but a container ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:36.34,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Please zip it. I won't do it again. \NI promise I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:38.82,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it about time you told me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.10,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Who's calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:44.29,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's the manager, AKA Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:48.56,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling rather late. \NI'm sure you've got a lot on your plate,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.84,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,but time is money. \NThat's what you always tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:54.19,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get here soon, \Nit'll happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:56.90,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Meet me at the warehouse we \Nvisited the other day. See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.07,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,That's my gun. Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:04.78,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.83,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu. You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:09.33,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,Dobu? You're really him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:13.65,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? Kabasawa-sama's giving \Na million yen to anyone who catches you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.13,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a bounty on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:17.00,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You work for Kabasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.25,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, or I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:28.28,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,It's fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:30.39,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's the real gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.60,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.23,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good enough. I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:37.10,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who shot up \Nthe cabaret club, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.98,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that you? I'm just cosplaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.28,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.22,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.22,Default,SKULL,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:48.73,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where the hell is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:50.00,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.38,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dobu. On the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:52.25,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kabasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:53.29,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,That asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:04.26,Default,DOBU,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:08.48,Default,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:13.90,Default,SEKIGUCHI,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Yano-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.18,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Mr. Sekiguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:18.48,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,That track suit looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:21.04,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,It's looking more and more \Nlike it'll come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:24.50,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,In accordance with fundamentalism, \NI'll see it all through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:27.32,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,The violence of the present \Nsituation is just the preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:29.88,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the next stage. \NLet's keep it flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:33.18,Default,YANO,0000,0000,0000,,So, Eiji Kakihana, how's everything going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:50.61,Next_Time,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: {\fs22\b1}Bless you{\fs\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.77,0:23:38.17,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So, is your job search going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:40.00,Italics,KABASAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm having trouble deciding what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:42.48,Italics,KABASAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't know how I feel about \Nworking for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:45.77,Italics,KABASAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I can't forget the elation I felt then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.65,Italics,ODOKAWA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You really did let yourself \Nget carried away.